# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# SQLNEW — conversational one-LLM SQL pipeline
#
# This repo is intentionally self-contained: a fresh clone runs with NO rebuild.
# The following generated/data files ARE committed on purpose (do not ignore them):
#   data/sales.db                       bundled read-only source database (~4 MB)
#   skills/sales/knowledge.db           knowledge base — source of truth (pre-seeded)
#   skills/sales/skill.md               rendered documentation view
#   skills/sales/embedding_docs.jsonl   exported embedding docs
#   skills/sales/schema_snapshot.json   schema snapshot
#   skills/sales/metadata.json          build metadata
#   skills/sales/index/                 prebuilt Qwen vector index (vectors.npy + meta.json)
#                                       so retrieval works without a GPU re-embed on setup
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# ---- Python ----
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*.egg-info/
.eggs/
.pytest_cache/
.mypy_cache/
.ruff_cache/

# ---- Virtual environments (create your own after cloning) ----
.venv/
venv/
env/
ENV/

# ---- Local config / secrets (keep .env.example, which IS committed) ----
.env
.env.local
.env.*.local

# ---- Node / frontend ----
frontend/node_modules/
frontend/dist/
frontend/.vite/
npm-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*

# ---- Runtime-generated data (recreated automatically; NOT source) ----
# Conversation memory is created empty on the first chat turn.
skills/sales/conversations.db
# Structured log output (LOG_FILE, default logs/app.jsonl; rotating).
logs/
# SQLite WAL / shared-memory / rollback sidecars for ANY .db (incl. the committed ones).
*.db-wal
*.db-shm
*.db-journal

# ---- OS / editor junk ----
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini
.idea/
.vscode/
*.swp
*~
